        <p class="govuk-body">
          The GOV.UK Design System is maintained by the Government Digital Service.
          If you’ve got a question, idea or suggestion you can:
        </p>
        <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet govuk-!-mb-r0">
        <li>
          <a href="mailto:govuk-design-system-support@digital.cabinet-office.gov.uk" class="govuk-link" data-hsupport="email">
            email the Design System team
          </a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://ukgovernmentdigital.slack.com/messages/govuk-design-system" class="govuk-link" data-hsupport="slack">
            get in touch on Slack</a> (<a class="govuk-link" href="slack://channel?team=T04V6EBTR&amp;id=C6DMEH5R6" data-hsupport="slackapp">open in app</a>)
